OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775192647
OL,3,CManned mission to Moon fires engines
OL,4,Cto leave Earth's orbit
OL,6,FNasa's first manned Moon mission in
OL,7,Fmore than five decades fired its
OL,8,Frockets early on Friday to break out
OL,9,Fof Earth's orbit.
OL,11,FNasa deputy associate administrator
OL,12,FLori Glaze told a news conference:
OL,13,F"Ladies and gentlemen, I am so, so
OL,14,Fexcited to be able to tell you that
OL,15,Ffor the first time since 1972 during
OL,16,FApollo 17, human beings have left
OL,17,FEarth orbit."
OL,26,@uD@AOUyD@MO]
