FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775192647
OL,3,CManned mission to Moon fires engines
OL,4,Cto leave Earth's orbit
OL,6,FThe four astronauts on the Artemis II
OL,7,Fmission, which launched from Cape
OL,8,FCanaveral in Florida on Wednesday
OL,9,Fevening, spent the first 25 hours of
OL,10,Fthe flight circling the Earth.
OL,12,FFiring the rockets on the Orion
OL,13,Fspacecraft ` officially called a
OL,14,Ftranslunar injection burn ` will send
OL,15,Fthem towards the Moon, which they will
OL,16,Fcircle before returning to Earth.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
