FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775192647
OL,3,CManned mission to Moon fires engines
OL,4,Cto leave Earth's orbit
OL,6,FCanadian astronaut Jeremy Hansen said
OL,7,Fthe crew, which also includes
OL,8,FCommander Reid Wiseman, pilot Victor
OL,9,FGlover and Christina Koch, had been
OL,10,Fglued to the windows to see the
OL,11,F"phenomenal" view.
OL,13,FHe said: "Humanity has once again
OL,14,Fshown what we are capable of, and it's
OL,15,Fyour hopes for the future that carry
OL,16,Fus now on this journey around the
OL,17,Fmoon."
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@LO]uD@JOUyD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
